<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉sẖrq yạ ạllh ʿlynạ ạ̉sẖrq fynạ wḥwạlynạ
 sẖʿbk nḥn nryd rḍạk fạḥḍr bạlạ̉mjạd ạ̹lynạ
 1- ạ̹nạ nṭlb wjhk ḥqạaⁿ bqlwb ttklm ṣdqạaⁿ
 qd tbnạ lnsyr wrạk nsʿy̱ kẖlf ạlqṣd ạlạ̉nqy̱
 ạ̹nạ nṭlb brk wḥdk lsnạ nṭlb sẖyỷạaⁿ bʿdk
 ạ̹rfʿnạ ʿndk lsmạk ạ̉w ạ̉nzlhạ nbṣr mjdk
 2- ạ̹nạ nṭlb mạ tṭlbh mhmạ tbgẖḍ lạ nrgẖbh
 ạ̹n nnsẖd mʿ mwsyqạk ạ̉y nsẖạz lạ nrgẖbh
 ạ̉sẖrq yạ ạllh dwạmạaⁿ ẓll fwq bnyk slạmạaⁿ
 ạ̉sknạ fy str ḥmạk wạ̉ntẖr fy ạlạ̉jwạʾ wỷạmạaⁿ</lyrics>
